column5: The last few weeks anywhere within an one hour drive of Mtl. the smallies are on fire. 30 t0 70 fish a day is the normal with plenty of big 5"s. One day our 5 best was i oz. shy of 27lbs. Enjoy...
you should come to simcoe and get the really big ones..    just kidding   nice fish there
Terry, be nice now.   Very nice fish .
Just remember Larry.........  I'm a Pm away......Whitespinnerbait..AKA ...Bass Addict..
Very impressive smallies for sure. Thanks for sharing.
